RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Battle Ground, WA operates under a Council-Manager plan of government. The City Council is a seven-member elected board, and the Mayor and Deputy Mayor are selected by the City Council from among its members for two-year terms. Troy McCoy was selected as Mayor and Shane Bowman as Deputy Mayor, both beginning January 2024. There was a discrepancy in sources regarding the Council Member for Position No. 4; the official city website lists Jeanie Kuypers, while other recent news articles mention Adrian Cortes. The official city website's listing has been prioritized for this response.
